There are a few different ways to see that this ratio is $\boxed{\frac{1}{2}}$.
One way is to note that we can divide $ABC$ into 4 congruent triangles, 2 of which are shaded: [asy]
defaultpen(1);
pair C=(0,0), A=(0,3), B=(4,0);
