Let $P$ be a point such that $OP = 12,$ and let $\theta = \angle AOP.$  Let $Q$ be the midpoint of $\overline{AP}.$

[asy]
unitsize(4 cm);

pair A, O, P, Q;

A = (1,0);
O = (0,0);
P = dir(40);
Q = (A + P)/2;

draw(A--O--P--cycle);
